\c 26
\s UPawuli uziphendulela phambi kukaFestusi loAgripha
\p
\v 1 UAgripha wasesithi kuPawuli: Uvunyelwe ukuzikhulumela. UPawuli waseselula isandla, waziphendulela \add wathi\x + 26.2,24. 19.33.\x*\add*:
\v 2 Kukho konke engimangalelwa ngakho ngamaJuda\x + 26.7. 19.38.\x*, nkosi Agripha, ngizizwa ngithokoza ukuthi sengingaziphendulela phambi kwakho lamuhla\x + 26.2,24. 19.33.\x*;
\v 3 ikakhulu ngikwazi uyisazi sawo wonke amasiko lokuphikisana phakathi kwamaJuda\x + 6.14.\x*; ngakho ngiyakuncenga, ukuthi ungizwe ngesineke.
\v 4 Ngakho ukuhamba kwami konke kusukela ebutsheni, okwakuqala esizweni sakithi eJerusalema, wonke amaJuda ayakwazi,
\v 5 ayangazi phambili kusukela ekuqaleni\x + Luka 1.3.\x*, uba bethanda ukufakaza\x + Mat. 25.24.\x*, ukuthi ngendlela eqinileyo\x + 22.3.\x* yehlelo lokukhonza kwakithi\x + Jak. 1.26,27.\x* ngaphila ngingumFarisi\x + 23.6. Fil. 3.5.\x*.
\v 6 Lakhathesi ngimi ngithonisiswa ngenxa yethemba\x + Luka 2.25. Seb. 23.6.\x* lesithembiso esenziwa nguNkulunkulu kubobaba\x + Luka 24.27. Seb. 13.32.\x*,
\v 7 ezithemba ukufinyelela kuso izizwe zakithi ezilitshumi lambili\x + Jak. 1.1.\x*, zikhonza\x + Luka 7.4. Seb. 12.5.\x* ngesineke ebusuku lemini\x + 24.14. 27.23.\x*; engimangalelwe ngalelithemba\x + Fil. 3.11.\x*, nkosi Agripha, ngamaJuda\x + 26.7. 19.38.\x*.
\v 8 Kungani kukhunjulwa ukuthi ku\add yinto\add* engakholekiyo kini, nxa uNkulunkulu evusa abafileyo?
\v 9 Ngakho lami ngokwami ngangicabanga ukuthi ngangifanele ukwenza izinto ezinengi eziphambene lebizo likaJesu weNazaretha\x + 1 Tim. 1.13.\x*;
\v 10 lami engakwenza eJerusalema\x + 8.3.\x*, njalo mina ngavalela abanengi kwabangcwele entolongweni\x + 9.13.\x*, sengemukele amandla avela kubapristi abakhulu\x + 9.14,21. 22.4, 5.\x*; lalapho bebulawa ngakukhetha\x + 22.20.\x*.
\v 11 Lemasinagogeni wonke ngabajezisa kanengi, nga\add ba\add*bamba ngamandla ukuthi bahlambaze\x + 22.19. Mat. 10.17.\x*; njalo ngahlanya kakhulu ngabo\x + 9.1,2.\x*, nga\add ba\add*zingela baze bafika emizini yabezizwe.
\v 12 Okungazo\x + Luka 12.1. Seb. 24.18.\x* lami ngisiya eDamaseko ngamandla langokuthunywa ngabapristi abakhulu,
\v 13 emini enkulu, nkosi, ngabona endleleni ukukhanya kuvela ezulwini, kudlula ukukhanya kwelanga, kwakhanya kwangizingelezela lalabo ababehamba lami\x + 9.3-8. 22.6-11.\x*.
\v 14 Kwathi sonke sesiwele phansi emhlabathini, ngezwa ilizwi likhuluma lami lisithi ngolimi lwesiHebheru: Sawuli, Sawuli, ungizingelelani? Kulukhuni kuwe ukukhahlelana lezincijo\x + 21.40.\x*.
\v 15 Mina ngasengisithi: Ungubani, Nkosi? Wasesithi: Mina nginguJesu omzingelayo.
\v 16 Kodwa sukuma, njalo ume ngenyawo zakho; ngoba ngibonakelele lokho kuwe, ukuthi ngikumise\x + 22.14.\x* ube yisikhonzi\x + Luka 1.2.\x* lomfakazi wezinto ozibonileyo, kanye lengizazibonakalisa ngazo kuwe\x + 22.15. 20.21,24.\x*,
\v 17 ngikophula ebantwini lakwabezizwe, engikuthuma kubo khathesi\x + 22.21. 28.28.\x*,
\v 18 ukuvula amehlo abo\x + Isa. 29.18. 32.3. 35.5. 42.7. Efe. 1.18.\x*, loku\add ba\add*phendula emnyameni \add ba\add*ye ekukhanyeni\x + Hlab. 36.9. Luka 1.79. Joha. 8.12. 2 Kor. 4.4. 6.14. Efe. 4.18. 5.8. 1 Thes. 5.5. 1 Pet. 2.9.\x*, lemandleni kaSathane \add ba\add*ye kuNkulunkulu\x + Luka 22.53.\x*, ukuze bemukeliswe uthethelelo lwezono\x + 5.31.\x*, lelifa phakathi kwabangcwelisiweyo ngokholo olukimi\x + 20.32. Mat. 25.34.\x*.
\v 19 Ngakho, nkosi Agripha, kangalanga ukulalela umbono wezulwini;
\v 20 kodwa ngatshumayela kuqala kwabaseDamaseko\x + 9.20,22.\x* labeJerusalema\x + 9.29.\x*, lakulo lonke ilizwe leJudiya\x + 11.26.\x*, lakwabezizwe, ukuze baphenduke\x + 13.46.\x*, babuyele kuNkulunkulu\x + 15.19.\x*, benze imisebenzi efanele ukuphenduka\x + Mat. 3.8.\x*.
\v 21 Ngenxa yalezizinto amaJuda angibamba ethempelini, azama uku\add ngi\add*bulala\x + 21.27,30,31. 24.18.\x*.
\v 22 Ngakho ngizuzile usizo oluvela kuNkulunkulu, kuze kube lamuhla ngimi ngifakaza kubo bonke abancinyane labakhulu\x + Isam. 11.18. 13.16. 19.5,18. 20.12. Seb. 8.10. Jer. 6.13.\x*, ngingakhulumi lutho ngaphandle kwalezozinto abazikhulumayo abaprofethi\x + Luka 24.27,44. Seb. 10.43. 13.27. 24.14. 28.23.\x* loMozisi\x + Luka 24.27,44. Seb. 10.43. 13.27. 24.14. 28.23.\x* ukuthi zizakwenzeka,
\v 23 ukuthi uKristu umele ukuhlupheka\x + Mat. 26.24.\x*, \add lo\add*kuthi engowokuqala ekuvukeni kwabafileyo\x + 1 Kor. 15.20,23. Kol. 1.18. Isam. 1.5.\x* uzatshumayela ukukhanya kulababantu lakwabezizwe\x + Luka 2.32.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Kwathi esaziphendulela lezizinto\x + 26.1.\x*, uFestusi wathi ngelizwi elikhulu: Uyahlanya, Pawuli\x + 26.25. 2 Kho. 9.11. 1 Kor. 1.23. 2.14. 4.10.\x*; ukufunda okunengi kuyakuhlanyisa\x + Joha. 7.15.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa wathi: Kangihlanyi\x + 2 Kor. 5.13.\x*\x + 26.25. 2 Kho. 9.11. 1 Kor. 1.23. 2.14. 4.10.\x*, mhlekazi Festusi\x + Luka 1.3.\x*, kodwa ngimemezela amazwi aliqiniso laqondileyo\x + 2 Kor. 5.13.\x*.
\v 26 Ngoba inkosi iyazi ngalezizinto, engikhuluma ngesibindi lakuyo\x + 4.29.\x*; ngoba ngileqiniso lokuthi akukho okunye kwalezizinto okufihlakeleyo kuyo; ngoba lokhu kakwenziwanga engonsini.
\v 27 Nkosi Agripha, uyakholwa abaprofethi yini? Ngiyazi ukuthi uyakholwa.
\v 28 UAgripha wasesithi kuPawuli: Usuphose wangiqinisekisa ukuthi ngibe ngumKristu\x + 11.26. 1 Pet. 4.16.\x*.
\v 29 UPawuli wasesithi: Bengingafisa kuNkulunkulu ukuthi, loba ngokulutshwana loba ngokunengi kungabi nguwe wedwa, kodwa labo bonke abangizwayo lamuhla, babe ngabanje njengoba nginjalo lami, ngaphandle kwalezizibopho\x + 22.30. 2 Tim. 2.9. Seb. 21.33. 28.20.\x*.
\v 30 Kwathi esekhulume lezizinto, yasukuma inkosi, lombusi\x + Mat. 27.2.\x*, loBernike\x + 25.23.\x*, lalabo ababehlezi labo\x + 25.23.\x*;
\v 31 kwathi sebephumile bakhulumisana, besithi: Lumuntu kenzi lutho olufanele ukufa kumbe ukubotshwa\x + 23.29. 25.25. 23.9.\x*.
\v 32 UAgripha wasesithi kuFestusi: Lumuntu ubengakhululwa\x + 28.18.\x*, uba ebengalidluliselanga kuKesari\x + 25.11,12,21,25. 28.19.\x*.
